<refsect1 xml:id='description'><title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<para><function>Tk_GetHWND</function> returns the Windows HWND identifier for X Windows
window given by <emphasis remap='I'>window</emphasis>.</para>

<para><function>Tk_AttachHWND</function> binds the Windows HWND identifier to the
specified Tk_Window given by <emphasis remap='I'>tkwin</emphasis>. It returns an X Windows
window that encapsulates the HWND.</para>

</refsect1>

